## 🔧 Environment Variables

| Variable       | Description                 |
| -------------- | --------------------------- |
| API_BASE_URL   | Base URL of the environment |
| MODEL_NAME     | LLM model identifier        |
| HF_TOKEN       | Hugging Face / API key      |
| OPENAI_API_KEY | OpenAI API key              |

